[I] Compiler infrastructure and toolchain library for WebAssembly, in C++

[T] Binaryen is a compiler and toolchain infrastructure library for
[T] WebAssembly, written in C++. It aims to make compiling to WebAssembly easy,
[T] fast, and effective.

[U] https://github.com/WebAssembly/binaryen

